    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:1.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—",
          "en": "So I have heard. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:1.2",
          "pli": "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā uruvelāyaṃ viharati najjā nerañjarāya tīre ajapālanigrodhamūle paṭhamābhisambuddho. ",
          "en": "At one time, when he was first awakened, the Buddha was staying near Uruvelā at the root of the goatherd’s banyan tree on the bank of the Nerañjarā River. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:1.3",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā rattandhakāratimisāyaṃ abbhokāse nisinno hoti, devo ca ekamekaṃ phusāyati. ",
          "en": "Now at that time the Buddha was meditating in the open during the dark of night, while a gentle rain drizzled down. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:1.4",
          "pli": "Atha kho māro pāpimā, bhagavato bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo, yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato avidūre uccāvacā vaṇṇanibhā upadaṃseti, subhā ceva asubhā ca. ",
          "en": "Then Māra the Wicked, wanting to make the Buddha feel fear, terror, and goosebumps, approached him, and while not far away generated a rainbow of bright colors, both beautiful and ugly. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:1.5",
          "pli": "Atha kho bhagavā “māro ayaṃ pāpimā” iti viditvā māraṃ pāpimantaṃ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi: ",
          "en": "Then the Buddha, knowing that this was Māra the Wicked, replied to him in verse: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:2.1",
          "pli": "“Saṃsaraṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ, ",
          "en": "“Transmigrating for such a long time, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:2.2",
          "pli": "vaṇṇaṃ katvā subhāsubhaṃ; ",
          "en": "you’ve made forms beautiful and ugly. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:2.3",
          "pli": "Alaṃ te tena pāpima, ",
          "en": "Enough of this, Wicked One! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:2.4",
          "pli": "nihato tvamasi antaka. ",
          "en": "You’re beaten, terminator. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:3.1",
          "pli": "Ye ca kāyena vācāya, ",
          "en": "Those who are well restrained "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:3.2",
          "pli": "manasā ca susaṃvutā; ",
          "en": "in body, speech, and mind "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:3.3",
          "pli": "Na te māravasānugā, ",
          "en": "don’t fall under Māra’s sway, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:3.4",
          "pli": "na te mārassa baddhagū”ti. ",
          "en": "they don’t become your footmen.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.3:4.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho māro … pe … tatthevantaradhāyīti. ",
          "en": "Then Māra … vanished right there."
        }
      ],
